==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} [[invocare]], to call upon

===Verb===
'''to invoke'''

# {{transitive}} To [[call]] upon someone for [[help]], [[assistance]] or [[guidance]], especially upon a [[god]].
# {{transitive}} To [[conjure]] up with [[incantation]]s.
# {{transitive}} {{computing}} To call a [[program]] or [[subroutine]].

